data.name: HelpTip_ChangePassword_2
data.value: The option to change login password is located in top bar. Clicking in “Admin” will show a drop menu where it's possible to change your password and also logout from mega-X Configuration Tool.

data.name: HelpTip_DownloadUpload_2
data.value: It's possible to make Upload/Download to/for mega-X in a faster way. Using top right buttons of each configuration category will make a partial upload or download.

data.name: HelpTip_ElementConfig_2
data.value: You can configure a single element by double-clicking on it row on any table on any menu. This will open a new window where you can configure only that element in an easier way. It's also possible to access this window using the menu on left side of the app.

data.name: HelpTip_Language_2
data.value: It's possible to change language between english (en-US) and portuguese (pt-PT) in Preferences menu or in login window when starting mega-X Configuration Tool.

data.name: HelpTip_Wizard_2
data.value: When creating a new file it's possible to be assisted by a Wizard to make it in a easier and intuitive way. This Wizard will help you start a new configuration project for mega-X.
